  <ThingDef ParentName="RC2_PlantBase" Name="RC2_TomatoBase" Abstract="True">
    <label>tomato plant</label>
    <description>This bright red bulb is the fruit of a deadly strain of poisonous plants.  The fruit itself is not poisonous, thankfully, and is actually quite delicious, especially when cooked into a sauce or made into ketchup.  Although a fruit, the Toma Mato is classified as a vegetable by chefs.  They donâ€™t know any better.  Likes temperate climates.</description>
